Comando para compilar C++ con opencv
g++ `pkg-config --cflags opencv` codename.cpp `pkg-config --libs opencv` -o codename

http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=2151251
11/11/2013



gcc --shared -I/usr/lib/jvm/java-7-openjdk-i386/include `pkg-config --cflags opencv` Libcvideo.c `pkg-config --libs opencv` -o libcvideo.so

